# Common Interview Mistakes

❌ Java is an interpreted language.

✅ Java is compiled into bytecode, which is executed by the JVM.

---

❌ Java was created only for enterprise applications.

✅ It was originally designed for consumer electronic devices and later became widely used for enterprise applications.

---

❌ Robust means Java never throws errors.

✅ Robust means Java provides Exception Handling and Garbage Collection to make applications more reliable.

---

❌ WORA means Java runs without JVM.

✅ Java requires a compatible JVM to execute bytecode.

